		{
			dependencies: [
				"VL01000000000003"
				"07B89901B2D44559"
			]
			description: ["Your soul has expanded beyond the limits of a single world. The Spirit Ancestor confirms what the dimensional resonance has been whispering: the walls between planes are thin, and yours is a form capable of passing through them."]
